data.title: Sir Ferdinand von Mueller
data.meta_description: #SirFerdinandvonMueller, #botanist, #Australia Ferdiand Mueller grows up and starts to work on botany in Tönning, a small town at the North Sea. Later he became the most famous natural scientist in Australia of the 19th century.
